precis:
THE PAS AIRPORT ZONING REGULATIONS limiting the height of new
buildings, structures, and objects or additions to any existing buildings,
structures or objects, including objects of natural growth, and will
prohibit the disposal of any waste edible by or attractive to birds on
lands adjacent to the airport.
